original_title: Ty Me Up, Ty Me Down
overview: Ty Roderick... Just saying his name conjures up thoughts and feelings of dominant intensity. When Ty enters a room, you just know -- you can feel -- that he takes no prisoners. He'll slam you into the bed, against a wall, or on your knees... and take you. Oh did we mention his VOICE? #Dead! Including Asher Hawk, JD Phoenix & Max Ryder, this DVD contains some of Ty's best performances.
title: Ty Me Up, Ty Me Down
